<paragraph blockId="60.[187,1400,311,478]" lastBlockId="61.[187,1401,265,651]" lastPageId="61" lastPageNumber="62" pageId="60" pageNumber="61">
Critically Endangered: CR B2ab(iii). 
<taxonomicName authority="Block, 2022" authorityName="De Block" authorityYear="2022" box="[642,950,311,337]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rubiaceae" genus="Paracephaelis" kingdom="Plantae" order="Gentianales" pageId="60" pageNumber="61" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="ranirisonii" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis box="[642,950,311,337]" italics="true" pageId="60" pageNumber="61">Paracephaelis ranirisonii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[959,1052,312,338]" pageId="60" pageNumber="61" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
is only known from a single collection, which means that the extent of occurrence (EOO) cannot be calculated. The area of occupancy (AOO) is 
<quantity box="[306,365,381,408]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.0" pageId="60" pageNumber="61" unit="km" value="4.0">4 km</quantity>
<superScript attach="right" box="[367,376,381,395]" fontSize="6" pageId="60" pageNumber="61">2</superScript>
, which complies with the Critically Endangered status under criterion B2. The species is known from a single location, which also complies with the Critically Endangered status under sub criterion ‘a’ of criterion B2. The 
<typeStatus box="[579,630,452,478]" pageId="60" pageNumber="61">type</typeStatus>
specimen was collected recently (2004) in the Loky-Manambato Protected Landscape (Daraina). The region of Loky-Manambato is very diverse in altitude and rainfall, hence a mosaic of different forest 
<typeStatus box="[571,632,301,327]" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">types</typeStatus>
occurs, from dry to humid evergreen, and from lowland to montane forest (
<bibRefCitation author="Nusbaumer L. &amp; Ranirison P. &amp; Gautier L. &amp; Chatelain C. &amp; Loizeau P. - A. &amp; Spichiger R." box="[269,540,337,363]" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" pagination="253 - 264" refId="ref69593" refString="Nusbaumer L., Ranirison P., Gautier L., Chatelain C., Loizeau P. - A. &amp; Spichiger R. 2010. Loky- Manambato: point de rencontre des principales unites phytogeographiques de Madagascar. In: van der Burgt X., van der Maesen J. &amp; Onana J. - M. (eds) Systematique et Conservation des Plantes Africaines: 253 - 264. Royal Botanic Gardens, Kew." type="book chapter" year="2010">
Nusbaumer 
<emphasis box="[412,470,337,363]" italics="true" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">et al.</emphasis>
2010
</bibRefCitation>
). Loky-Manambato is known for its high species diversity and endemicity (
<bibRefCitation author="Rakotondravony H. A." box="[195,461,373,399]" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" pagination="15 - 18" refId="ref69985" refString="Rakotondravony H. A. 2006. Aspects de la conservation des reptiles et des amphibiens dans la region de Daraina. Madagascar Conservation &amp; Development 1: 15 - 18. https: // doi. org / 10.4314 / mcd. v 1 i 1.44118" type="journal article" year="2006">Rakotondravony 2006</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Nusbaumer L. &amp; Ranirison P. &amp; Gautier L. &amp; Chatelain C. &amp; Loizeau P. - A. &amp; Spichiger R." box="[472,741,373,399]" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" pagination="253 - 264" refId="ref69593" refString="Nusbaumer L., Ranirison P., Gautier L., Chatelain C., Loizeau P. - A. &amp; Spichiger R. 2010. Loky- Manambato: point de rencontre des principales unites phytogeographiques de Madagascar. In: van der Burgt X., van der Maesen J. &amp; Onana J. - M. (eds) Systematique et Conservation des Plantes Africaines: 253 - 264. Royal Botanic Gardens, Kew." type="book chapter" year="2010">
Nusbaumer 
<emphasis box="[614,672,373,399]" italics="true" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">et al.</emphasis>
2010
</bibRefCitation>
). As a region of transition it is of high conservation value (
<bibRefCitation author="Nicoll M. E. &amp; Langrand O." box="[195,483,409,435]" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" refId="ref69502" refString="Nicoll M. E. &amp; Langrand O. 1989. Madagascar: Revue de la Conservation et des Aires protegees. World Wide Fund for Nature, Gland, Switzerland." type="book" year="1989">Nicoll &amp; Langrand 1989</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Ganzhorn J. U. &amp; Rakotosamimanana B. &amp; Hannah L. &amp; Hough J. &amp; Iyer L. &amp; Olivieri S. &amp; Rajaobelina S. &amp; Rodstrom C. &amp; Tilkin G." box="[493,737,409,435]" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" pagination="1 - 81" refId="ref67964" refString="Ganzhorn J. U., Rakotosamimanana B., Hannah L., Hough J., Iyer L., Olivieri S., Rajaobelina S., Rodstrom C. &amp; Tilkin G. 1997. Priorities for biodiversity conservation in Madagascar. Primate Report 48: 1 - 81." type="book chapter" year="1997">
Ganzhorn 
<emphasis box="[613,670,409,435]" italics="true" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">et al.</emphasis>
1997
</bibRefCitation>
). While nominally protected within the Loky-Manambato Protected Landscape, 
<taxonomicName authority="Block, 2022" authorityName="De Block" authorityYear="2022" box="[461,622,445,470]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rubiaceae" genus="Paracephaelis" kingdom="Plantae" order="Gentianales" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="ranirisonii" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis box="[461,622,445,470]" italics="true" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">P. ranirisonii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[631,726,445,471]" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
is threatened by habitat loss as a result of clearing for subsistence farming, burning for pasture, logging for timber and charcoal, and artisanal mining for gold (
<bibRefCitation author="Rakotondravony H. A." box="[196,464,516,542]" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" pagination="52 - 65" refId="ref70032" refString="Rakotondravony H. A. 2009. Reptiles, amphibiens et gradient altitudinal dans la region de Daraina, extreme nord-est de Madagascar. Malagasy Nature 2: 52 - 65. Available from http: // www. vahatra. mg / volume 2 / mn 02 _ 03. pdf [accessed 1 Jul. 2021]." type="journal article" year="2009">Rakotondravony 2009</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Nusbaumer L. &amp; Ranirison P. &amp; Gautier L. &amp; Chatelain C. &amp; Loizeau P. - A. &amp; Spichiger R." box="[476,750,516,542]" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" pagination="253 - 264" refId="ref69593" refString="Nusbaumer L., Ranirison P., Gautier L., Chatelain C., Loizeau P. - A. &amp; Spichiger R. 2010. Loky- Manambato: point de rencontre des principales unites phytogeographiques de Madagascar. In: van der Burgt X., van der Maesen J. &amp; Onana J. - M. (eds) Systematique et Conservation des Plantes Africaines: 253 - 264. Royal Botanic Gardens, Kew." type="book chapter" year="2010">
Nusbaumer 
<emphasis box="[619,678,516,542]" italics="true" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">et al.</emphasis>
2010
</bibRefCitation>
). Therefore, a reduction in the extent and quality of the habitat of 
<taxonomicName authority="Block, 2022" authorityName="De Block" authorityYear="2022" box="[309,465,553,578]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rubiaceae" genus="Paracephaelis" kingdom="Plantae" order="Gentianales" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="ranirisonii" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis box="[309,465,553,578]" italics="true" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">P. ranirisonii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[472,563,553,579]" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
is inferred. This fact, in combination with the low AOO and the single location, qualifies the species as Critically Endangered. For further details on the Loky-Manambato Protected Landscape, see 
<taxonomicName authority="Block, 2022" authorityName="De Block" authorityYear="2022" box="[492,614,625,650]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rubiaceae" genus="Paracephaelis" kingdom="Plantae" order="Gentianales" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="gautieri" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis box="[492,614,625,650]" italics="true" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">P. gautieri</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[621,712,625,651]" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</paragraph>
